title: Toya - Toya (2001)
description:
Toya's eponymous and only album ever released, most notable for the hit single "I Do!!", Toya was released in August 2001.  

This is an original TPB release, the first-ever full-quality release of this album.

Ripped with EAC, 320kbps.  

Note:  There is some clipping, but all audio is normalized to 100%.  Blame the people who mastered the album, not me.  Quality is much better than anything else out there so far.
